Even though it may be that researchers are able to record their
thoughts on media, I feel that in many cases it is because the
researcher becomes part of the recording mechanism through a form of
psychokinesis.

 It includes the the possibility that the researcher is actually in
communication with others in the spirit realm and is transferring the
thoughts and feeling of those other beings to the recording device.

-Bill

